{"id":"6950dffd4980fb579f1e04b5","title":"Galaxy Z TriFold 発表","image":null,"created":1766907902,"updated":1766907907,"lines":[{"id":"6950dffd4980fb579f1e04b5","text":"Galaxy Z TriFold 発表","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d38","text":"from [20251203] #1203","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907907},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d39","text":"[Galaxy Z TriFold] 発表","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3a","text":"[サムスン]が2025年12月に発表した「[Galaxy Z TriFold]」は、世界初の三つ折りスマートフォンです。本体を3つに折りたたむことで、コンパクトなスマートフォンから広げると10インチのタブレットサイズに変化し、マルチタスクや大画面コンテンツ視聴に最適化されています。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3b","text":"","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3c","text":"主な特徴","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3d","text":" 2つのヒンジを採用し、内側に2回折り畳む設計。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3e","text":" 展開時は10インチ（253mm）、折りたたみ時は6.5インチのディスプレイ。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d3f","text":" 折りたたみ時厚さは12.9mm、展開時最薄部は3.9mm。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d40","text":" バッテリーは5600mAhの3セルシステムで、45W急速充電対応。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d41","text":" プロセッサはSnapdragon 8 Elite Mobile Platform for Galaxy。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d42","text":" カメラは2億画素の広角カメラを搭載。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d43","text":" 重量は約309g。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d44","text":" 三つのパネルにそれぞれバッテリーを配置し、バランスの取れた電力供給を実現。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d45","text":" 折りたたみ機構にはチタン製ヒンジ「Armor FlexHinge」を採用。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d46","text":" 防水防塵性能はIP48等級。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d47","text":"","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d48","text":"価格と発売","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d49","text":" 韓国での価格は約359万ウォン（約38万円）。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4a","text":" 2025年12月12日に[韓国]で発売、その後[中国]、[台湾]、[シンガポール]、[UAE]、[米国]などにも順次展開予定。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4b","text":" [日本]発売は未定。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4c","text":"","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4d","text":"使い方とユニークな機能","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4e","text":" 展開時、最大3つのアプリを横並びで実行可能。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d4f","text":" タブレット版「[Samsung DeX]」をサポートし、PCライクな作業環境を提供。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d50","text":" 折りたたみ時の誤操作を防止する自動アラーム機能付き。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d51","text":" AI活用機能（Samsung Internetの要約・翻訳、Samsung HealthのUI向上）も搭載。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d52","text":"Galaxy Z TriFoldは、サムスンの折りたたみ技術の集大成であり、スマートフォンとタブレットのハイブリッドとして、マルチタスクやエンタメ用途に特化した新カテゴリーの端末です。","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d53","text":"[1 https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/a8c11f681c007220a49b0f18d7b632185c925e3a]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d54","text":"[2 https://k-tai.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/2067893.html]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d55","text":"[3 https://www.bloomberg.co.jp/news/articles/2025-12-02/T6MBANT9NJLT00]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d56","text":"[4 https://japan.cnet.com/article/35241085/]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d57","text":"[5 https://sumahodigest.com/?p=48239]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d58","text":"[6 https://jp.reuters.com/markets/global-markets/P4R3UENNFJKEDPZTSAHO6ZN2FQ-2025-12-02/]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d59","text":"[7 https://0115765.com/archives/160583]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d5a","text":"[8 https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZQOGM27AOS0X21C25A1000000/]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d5b","text":"[9 https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2512/03/news055.html]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d5c","text":"[10 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6NQQNG-upAI]","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902},{"id":"6950dffe0000000000df4d5d","text":"","created":1766907902,"updated":1766907902}]}